  "texts": [
    "With advancements in machine learning (ML) (supervised, self-supervised, and unsupervised), natural language processing (NLP), and computer vision, AI is increasingly capable of performing tasks that once required human expertise.",
    "These tools are powerful accelerants in multiple fields (Suleyman, 2023).",
    "The rapid ascent of AI raises important questions about how SLP will adapt to emerging technologies and what shifts may occur in professional roles and responsibilities.",
    "While foundational knowledge remains indispensable (Willingham, 2006), SLPs must address their reported hesitancy (Austin et al., 2025) and engage proactively with these technologies (Mollick, 2024).",
    "Calls for such engagement are growing within the literature (Cordella et al., 2025; Green, 2024)."
  ],
